a small team entirely dedicated to that end, and as such we are able to quickly createvaluablecontent each week based on the immediate needs of our customers. Our users are part of the family, so if you have any questions about our content, your projects, or anything else going on in your life, we\'d love to help -<a id=\"contact\" class=\"contactform\" title=\"Contact\" href=\"#\">email</a> or call (877.688.7563)..We\'ll get back to you as soon as humanly possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">The Team</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Just two dudes who are really passionate about SolidWorks, teaching people how to use it, and building great products.</p>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Rohit Mitra</h4>\r\n<h5>Founder, Content Guy</h5>\r\nI got my start with SolidWorks after joining (and eventually becoming project lead) of my college\'s Baja SAE team while studying mechanical engineering. After I graduated, I went to work for SolidWorks for a time before moving to the largest SolidWorks reseller to work in a technical support capacity. The best part of my day was helping customers design projects they are passionate about, so I started SolidWize to do that full time. I\'d love to hear from you, email me directly at Rohit@solidwize.com or follow me on <a title=\"Solidwize Twitter\" href=\"http://twitter.com/solidwize\">twitter</a>.\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">[/one_half]</h4>\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-463 alignright\" title=\"me1\" src=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/me1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"226\" style=\"box-shadow:2px 2px 5px black\"/>\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n<a href=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/andrewabout.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-643\" title=\"andrewabout\" src=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/andrewabout.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"226\" style=\"box-shadow:2px 2px 5px black\"/></a>\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Andrew O\'Neal</h4>\r\n<h5>Co-Founder, Biz Dev Guy</h5>\r\nOnce upon a time I worked for one of the largest talent agencies in entertainment. After becoming jaded to the whole industry, I returned to my Silicon Valley roots. My background is in product development and web marketing. I\'ve pushed several digital and physical products to market, and after watching Rohit use SolidWorks to model one of my projects, I realized the power of the incredible tool and decided to help him teach others how to use it. Email me at andrew@solidwize.com, any time.\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">[/one_half_last]</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about-2','','','2012-07-12 17:06:30','2012-07-13 00:06:30','',0,'http://solidwize.com/?page_id=410',0,'page','',0),(411,2,'2012-02-12 21:51:23','2012-02-13 05:51:23','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','410-revision','','','2012-02-12 21:51:23','2012-02-13 05:51:23','',410,'http://solidwize.com/2012/410-revision',0,'revision','',0),(266,2,'2011-06-16 09:33:11','2011-06-16 16:33:11','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[chargify]</p>','Sign Up','','inherit','open','open','','93-revision-5','','','2011-06-16 09:33:11','2011-06-16 16:33:11','',93,'http://solidwize.com/post-name',0,'revision','',0),(338,2,'2011-11-30 20:39:39','2011-12-01 04:39:39',' ','','','publish','open','open','','338','','','2012-06-14 15:51:50','2012-06-14 22:51:50','',0,'http://solidwize.com/?p=338',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(272,2,'2011-11-09 10:33:00','2011-11-09 18:33:00','<h5>Last Updated: October 1st, 2011 </h5>\r\nSolidWize Engineering LLC (\"SolidWize\", \"we\" or \"our\") provides via our website, accessible at www.SolidWize.com (the \"Site\"), an online training platform through which users can access information and tutorials an