f we become aware that a child under 13 has provided us with Personal Information, we will delete such information from our files.\r\n<h5>Contacting Us</h5>\r\nIf you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at rohit@solidwize.com or at: SolidWize Engineering LLC  8335 Sunset Blvd., Suite 319, West Hollywood, CA 90069','Privacy Policy','','inherit','open','open','','168-revision-3','','','2011-11-04 14:16:12','2011-11-04 21:16:12','',168,'http://solidwize.com/168-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(349,2,'2011-12-13 19:04:39','2011-12-14 03:04:39','<h4 style=\"text-align: center; color: #014377;\">Are you a business? Contact me about <a id=\"contact-user\" href=\"#\">Business/Multi User Plans.</a></h4>\r\n</br>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; color: #014377;\">Still in school? Contact me about <a id=\"contact-student\" href=\"#\">Student Discounts.</a></h4>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #014377;\">What is included with my subscription?</h4>\r\nWhile you are actively subscribed to SolidWize training, you have unlimited access to all video tutorials and exercise files as well as any updates. This includes hours of training videos on the use of SolidWorks.\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #014377;\">How does your 7 day trial work?</h4>\r\nYou have 7 days of access to all SolidWize content, after which your credit card will be billed. Cancel at any time during the 7 day trial and your credit card will not be billed.\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #014377;\">How do I cancel service?</h4>\r\nAt the bottom of your user profile there is a cancellation option. Canceling a SolidWize subscription is an instantaneous and no questions asked process.\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #014377;\">How does your 30 day money back guarantee work?</h4>\r\nIf you are not 100% satisfied with your Membership, just email me before your first month has finished and I\'ll refund your money, no questions asked. If you\'re not happy I\'m not happy. Including the 7 day free trial that\'s a total of 37 days to try out my training.\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #014377;\">How often do you update your content?</h4>\r\nCurrently, I am adding new content weekly. If you\'d like to see any specific content added, please email me at <strong>rohit@solidwize.com.</strong>\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #014377;\">Any other questions?</h4>\r\n<a id=\"contact\" href=\"#\">Contact Me</a>, I\'ll be happy to answer any other questions you may have.\r\n\r\n[/one_half_last]','Pricing','','inherit','open','open','','261-revision-7','','','2011-12-13 19:04:39','2011-12-14 03:04:39','',261,'http://solidwize.com/2011/261-revision-7',0,'revision','',0),(262,2,'2011-11-18 12:03:26','2011-11-18 20:03:26','','Pricing','','inherit','open','open','','261-revision','','','2011-11-18 12:03:26','2011-11-18 20:03:26','',261,'http://solidwize.com/post-name',0,'revision','',0),(261,2,'2011-11-18 12:03:41','2011-11-18 20:03:41','<div id=\"pricingpagefaq\">\r\n<h4>Still in <strong>School</strong>? Check out our killer <a href=\"http://solidwize.com/students\">student discount.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>Are you a <strong>Business</strong>? Contact me about <a id=\"contact-user\" href=\"#\">business/multi-user plans.</a></h4>\r\n<br style=\"height: .25em;\" />\r\n[one_half]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"pricingfaq\">\r\n<h5>7 day trial you say?</h5>\r\nWith your subscription, you will have 7 days to access all of our great training content free of charge. After which, your credit card will automatically be billed. Cancel at any time during the 7 day trial, and you won\'t pay a thing.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pricingfaq2\">\r\n<h5>What\'s included with my subscription?</h5>\r\nWhile actively subscribed, you will have unlimited access to all video tutorials and exercise files (additional material added every Monday).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"pricingfaq2\">\r\n<h5>How do I cancel the service?</h5>\r\nWe\'d hate to see you go, but if you\'d like to cancel, just follow the link at