 to work in a technical support capacity. The best part of my day was helping customers design projects they are passionate about, so I started SolidWize to do that full time. I\'d love to hear from you, email me directly at Rohit@solidwize.com or follow me on <a title=\"Solidwize Twitter\" href=\"http://twitter.com/solidwize\">twitter</a>.\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">[/one_half]</h4>\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-463 alignright\" title=\"me1\" src=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/me1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"226\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n<a href=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/andrewabout.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-643\" title=\"andrewabout\" src=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/andrewabout.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"226\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Andrew O\'Neal</h4>\r\n<h5>Co-Founder, Biz Dev Guy</h5>\r\nOnce upon a time I worked for one of the largest talent agencies in entertainment. After becoming jaded to the whole industry, I returned to my Silicon Valley roots. My background is in product development and web marketing. I\'ve pushed several digital and physical products to market, and after watching Rohit use SolidWorks to model one of my projects, I realized the power of the incredible tool and decided to help him teach others how to use it. Email me at andrew@solidwize.com, any time.\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">[/one_half_last]</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','About','','inherit','open','open','','410-revision-11','','','2012-05-16 13:50:20','2012-05-16 20:50:20','',410,'http://solidwize.com/2012/410-revision-11',0,'revision','',0),(1013,2,'2012-07-05 18:21:16','2012-07-06 01:21:16','<a href=\"http://solidwize.com/2012/custom-sheet-format\"><img src=\"http://solidwize.com/solidwize/wp-content/uplo